{"tid":2510222,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"法國「政變」！幾十個退役將軍刊登聯署公開信，要求停止多元融合，以免法國落入伊斯蘭手中！","createTime":"2021-04-30T04:10:03.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-30T08:25:06.000Z","uid":28114,"like":83,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":38,"replies":[{"pid":"a950fa619a1a30b8591bd55c2583957c3295209c","tid":2510222,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T04:10:03.000Z","msg":"Generals call for military rule to halt France &lsquo;disintegrating with Islamists&rsquo;<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thetimes.co.uk/article/macron-dismisses-former-generals-warning-of-civil-war-in-france-qlzk9xs29\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thetimes.co.uk%2Farticle%2Fmacron-dismisses-former-generals-warning-of-civil-war-in-france-qlzk9xs29&d=SQXEpmicj55cx%2FeODTqnT1uXAffr%2FfAYLX%2F1af%2FGhNY%3D&h=03e7d7a0\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thetimes.co.uk/article/macron-dismisses-former-generals-warning-of-civil-war-in-france-qlzk9xs29</a><br />\n<br />\nThe Transformation of Marine Le Pen Has Macron&rsquo;s Allies Worried<br />\n<a href=\"https://uk.finance.yahoo.com/news/transformation-marine-le-pen-macron-030004662.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fuk.finance.yahoo.com%2Fnews%2Ftransformation-marine-le-pen-macron-030004662.html&d=SQXEpmicj55cx%2FeODTqnT1uXAffr%2FfAYLX%2F1af%2FGhNY%3D&h=3e7d42d5\" target=\"_blank\">https://uk.finance.yahoo.com/news/transformation-marine-le-pen-macron-030004662.html</a><br />\n<br />\nFrance vows to punish military signatories of rightwing &lsquo;call to arms&rsquo;<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ft.com/content/00f89665-3c70-4a52-99ab-2790eeae4b94?\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ft.com%2Fcontent%2F00f89665-3c70-4a52-99ab-2790eeae4b94%3F&d=SQXEpmicj55cx%2FeODTqnT1uXAffr%2FfAYLX%2F1af%2FGhNY%3D&h=91619b15\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ft.com/content/00f89665-3c70-4a52-99ab-2790eeae4b94?</a>"},{"pid":"a8d97f0ec006a9c078bc4433107dd91582b38c97","tid":2510222,"uid":28114,"like":20,"dislike":1,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T04:11:37.000Z","msg":"過半數法國人支持呢班將領<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmRNjTEuNkT2hR73nsTomCn7M4M9j6QJqnunfu91Q1pby3?filename=uereQjR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuereQjR.png&h=34593f45&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nA Harris Interactive opinion poll for LCI showed 58 per cent of French voters polled supported the military officers who signed the controversial declaration, compared with 42 per cent who were opposed. <br />\n<br />\nChart showing results of survey on support for the military signing the controversial declaration warning of the &lsquo;disintegration&rsquo; of France <br />\n<br />\nAmong respondents who said they supported a political party, 86 per cent of RN sympathisers backed the soldiers. For the centre-right Les R&eacute;publicains party, support was at 71 per cent, and even in Macron&rsquo;s La R&eacute;publique en Marche party it was at 46 per cent."},{"pid":"c2de29184229e0227e9dfa30324b9299b8530a0a","tid":2510222,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T04:18:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71e48630ab9171018f86c6be0a5b2bcf5b6ec383","tid":2510222,"uid":198792,"like":39,"dislike":0,"score":39,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T04:21:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmeN3S7ykU33iiHGVt1VpddSB5dVHG8qQ4Tr4QGuvU5dcH?filename=maDtaoi.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmaDtaoi.png&h=cfa4773a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"93ff1db9fdc9ef4ddd9a5f77be42fa74d7f525ce","tid":2510222,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"71e48630ab9171018f86c6be0a5b2bcf5b6ec383","tid":2510222,"uid":198792,"like":39,"dislike":0,"score":39,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T04:21:06.000Z"